WEBVTT

00:00.360 --> 00:02.332
To the left we have
our brand-new

00:02.866 --> 00:05.679
Enoch and Margaret Thompson
Pediatric Annex.

00:05.713 --> 00:07.849
- Please.
- Oh!

00:07.883 --> 00:10.756
Her baby's death, it could
easily have been prevented.

00:10.791 --> 00:13.030
Starting soon, I will be
accepting cash directly.

00:13.064 --> 00:14.834
<i>I have a middleman.</i>
<i>He'll be in touch.</i>

00:14.868 --> 00:16.335
We got company.

00:16.370 --> 00:19.478
You don't tell me when
the boss comes around?

00:21.182 --> 00:22.949
You and me, we had
our little fracas.

00:22.983 --> 00:25.086
Got off on the wombly
foot is all.

00:25.120 --> 00:28.057
- But we copacetic now.
- Sweet as Cracker Jack.

00:28.091 --> 00:29.827
Everything you do
is because I paid for it.

00:29.861 --> 00:31.997
Don't pretend you don't enjoy
playing the benefactor.

00:32.031 --> 00:34.134
You made me a benefactor
by giving that land away.

00:34.168 --> 00:38.138
I'm Lillian Kent,
but you can call me Billie.

00:38.172 --> 00:40.642
Already New Year's back home.

00:40.676 --> 00:43.113
Give my best to Katy.

00:44.517 --> 00:46.586
I want to welcome
Samuel to our table.

00:46.620 --> 00:49.791
Thank you, Mrs. White
and Mr. White.

00:49.826 --> 00:52.495
Effective immediately,
I'll be exporting exclusively

00:52.529 --> 00:53.529
<i>to Mr. Rothstein.</i>

00:53.565 --> 00:55.667
This is a business
decision, Mr. Rosetti.

00:55.702 --> 00:57.736
I need 500 cases of rum.

00:57.771 --> 01:00.608
You're making
my decision very easy.

01:00.642 --> 01:02.010
You'll plead guilty.

01:02.044 --> 01:04.914
<i>You'll do two years at the most.</i>

01:06.000 --> 01:12.074
